{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-archived-blog-template-js","path":"/2013/01/fotography-basic/","result":{"data":{"archivedBlogPostJson":{"categories":[{"path":"/category/learn/","name":"摄影学习与折腾"},{"path":"/category/film/","name":"独立电影与短片"}],"tags":[{"name":"光圈","path":"/tag/aperture/"},{"name":"快门速度","path":"/tag/shutter-speed/"},{"name":"感光度","path":"/tag/iso/"},{"name":"摄影","path":"/tag/photography/"},{"name":"教程","path":"/tag/tutorial/"}],"featured_media":{"source_url":"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/q.jpg"},"path":"/2013/01/fotography-basic/","date":"2013-01-08T13:25:22.000Z","excerpt":"1月5日19点30，在位于万达广场金街2楼的凯能数码影像俱乐部举办了一场针对摄影初学者的培训讲座，讲座内容简单 … ","title":"关于光圈 快门速度 感光度 摄影基础培训","content":"<p>1月5日19点30，在位于万达广场金街2楼的凯能数码影像俱乐部举办了一场针对摄影初学者的培训讲座，讲座内容简单的介绍了曝光的三个重要变量：光圈、快门速度、感光度ISO，最后分析了拍摄图片模糊的几个原因和排除办法。推荐是摄影初学者观看。</p>\n<p>主讲人凯能数码影像俱乐部负责人望超。</p>\n<p><object width=\"500\" height=\"375\" codebase=\"http://download.macromedia.com/pub/shockwave/cabs/flash/swflash.cab#version=6,0,40,0\" classid=\"clsid:d27cdb6e-ae6d-11cf-96b8-444553540000\"><param name=\"src\" value=\"http://player.youku.com/player.php/sid/XNDk4NDU2NTQ4/v.swf\"/><embed width=\"500\" height=\"375\" src=\"http://player.youku.com/player.php/sid/XNDk4NDU2NTQ4/v.swf\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\"/></object></p>\n<p>有任何关于摄影的问题请留言。</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2013/01/fotography-basic/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["251939775","3675143411","4019104361"]}